   gcd(54, 24) = 6
   gcd(7, 13) = 1
   gcd(100, 25) = 25
   gcd(12345, 67890) = 15

5. Least Common Multiple Examples:
   lcm(12, 18) = 36
   lcm(15, 20) = 60
   lcm(8, 12) = 24

