=== All numeric computations complete! ===

You can now test these scripts with your translator:
  ./sh2perl parse --perl examples/fibonacci.sh
  ./sh2perl parse --rust examples/factorize.sh
  ./sh2perl parse --python examples/primes.sh
  ./sh2perl parse --lua examples/gcd.sh
  ./sh2perl parse --js examples/numeric_computations.sh
